\b DESIGN DEFINITION
\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\li720\fi-720\sl264\slmult1\pardirnatural
\ls2\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}In my experience there is quite a bit of confusion around the term UX\
{\listtext	\'95	}It\'92s often defined as the visual design of a website\
{\listtext	\'95	}But to define UX as simply about the look and feel of a website is too narrow\
{\listtext	\'95	}It means that a good UX becomes the responsibility of a graphic designer who designs visuals\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\sl264\slmult1\pardirnatural
