\b JAKOB NIELSEN
\b0 \
\pard\tx220\tx720\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\li720\fi-720\sl264\slmult1\pardirnatural
\ls3\ilvl0\cf0 {\listtext	\'95	}The respected usability specialist, Jakob Nielsen, has a better definition for UX\
{\listtext	\'95	}\'93Every aspect of the user's interaction with a product, service, or company that make up the user's perceptions of the whole.\'94\
{\listtext	\'95	}This is a much broader definition of UX\
{\listtext	\'95	}He says everyone contributes to their user\'92s experience of their company\
{\listtext	\'95	}It also means UX is part of the development process, not a separate task by a designer in an agency\
{\listtext	\'95	}Whatever we build contributes in a small way to the user\'92s perception of CTM\
\pard\tx566\tx1133\tx1700\tx2267\tx2834\tx3401\tx3968\tx4535\tx5102\tx5669\tx6236\tx6803\sl264\slmult1\pardirnatural
